title: S15 Ep100: Homecoming: An Alien Abduction w/ Keith Blanchard
itunes:title: Homecoming: An Alien Abduction w/ Keith Blanchard
description:
Darkness Radio celebrates Thanksgiving with a Homecoming: An Alien Abduction with guest Keith Blanchard

Dave & Tim go to the outer limits today with guest Keith Blanchard to discuss his Alien Abduction. What was it like? Was it against his will? Why chose him? We will discuss these questions and more, but most importantly, are we in danger from these visitors or are they coming with a message?  Tune in to find out more.


Get the book here: https://amzn.to/3izJqDx
